  "caption": "Ever wonder how microservices talk to each other reliably and securely? A Service Mesh provides a transparent layer for traffic management, observability, and security policies without modifying your application code. It uses sidecar proxies to intercept and manage all network communication between services, making your distributed systems more resilient and easier to manage. Follow @byteflowlabs for daily systems & AI breakdowns.",
